{"tid":1995423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：應張宇人乞求及黨對港人的關切 已批增供港活豬配額","createTime":"2020-04-30T08:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T09:07:09.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18ed454f2c4982ae8d5fdd91a4a8ae51c6564d96","tid":1995423,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"商務部：隨活豬供應增 香港豬價急漲將緩解<br />\n30.04.2020 15:44<br />\n<br />\n今個月內地供港生豬拍賣價高企，在北京，商務部新聞發言人高峰表示， 主要是由於受非洲豬瘟疫情影響，出現生豬出欄暫時性短缺的情況，相信隨著內地生豬生產持續恢復，活豬供應數量有望進一步增加，豬肉價格過快上漲也會得到緩解。<br />\n<br />\n高峰強調，中央高度重視香港市場農副產品穩定供應，商務部已在年初足額下達供港活豬配額，根據監測，近期供港活豬數量已逐步恢復至日均1600至1700頭，拍賣價格回落至3月份平均水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284393&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284393%26csid%3D261_341&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=9c925210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284393&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fhuod2L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhuod2L.png&h=1c940654&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1169ba405303ea356c7fa272a2cbfc34b4ffb54d","tid":1995423,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，食開西班牙同丹麥豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a05bba17ce8110c5924a3836f43749f0676ad11","tid":1995423,"uid":148790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"唔反了，厲害了我的蝈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔反1個鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096000925dbce26ef0a67d0c028d0e5d3b0d1072"